# The Neutron · The nucleus's other resident — three quarks (up-down-down), no net charge. Stable inside a nucleus, but a FREE neutron decays in about 15 minutes (β-decay into a proton, electron, and antineutrino).

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

![silicon badge of The Neutron](neutron.silicon.png)
